rComments: Overall a good professor, definitely recommend him

Worst lecturer I ever had in U of T. All he does is copying word by word from Jason's notes on the black board (which is available on Quercus). Avoid his class by any means if you actually want to learn something about Linear Algebra.
Didn't explain anything, simply wrote on the board and talked about it as though we know what he's talking about: can't teach new concepts to people, even when prompted to elaborate of certain ideas.
